start_workflow.output_format:
Your output should include the initialized workflow state and initial tasks created:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "workflow": {
    "name": "Workflow name",
    "current_phase": "document_discovery",
    "start_time": "ISO timestamp",
    "input_files": ["List of input files"]
  },
  "initial_tasks": [
    {
      "task_id": "Task ID",
      "agent_id": "Agent ID",
      "description": "Task description",
      "status": "pending"
    }
  ]
}
```

advance_workflow.output_format:
Your output should include the updated workflow state and new tasks created:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "workflow": {
    "previous_phase": "Previous phase name",
    "current_phase": "New phase name",
    "transition_time": "ISO timestamp"
  },
  "new_tasks": [
    {
      "task_id": "Task ID",
      "agent_id": "Agent ID",
      "description": "Task description",
      "status": "pending"
    }
  ]
}
```

